WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
Start at the customer site and move from browsing to request submission.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
Select the vehicle card from the live fleet.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Open vehicle details before requesting dates.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Use the booking form on the vehicle detail page.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:12.500
Pick the pickup date.

00:00:12.500 --> 00:00:15.000
Pick the return date.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:17.500
Continue after dates are selected.

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.000
Confirm pickup or delivery details.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.500
Optional add-ons are selected here.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.000
Continue to customer details.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:27.500
Enter the customer first name.

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:30.000
Enter the customer last name.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.500
Enter the mobile phone for updates.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:35.000
Enter the customer email for confirmation.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:37.500
Review the request before submitting.

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:40.000
Submit the booking request.
